<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{طَائِفَةٌ}</span> ... جَمَاعَةٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَرْمُونَ}</span> ... يَقْذِفُونَ بِالزِّنَى.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمُحْصَنَاتِ}</span> ... العَفِيفَاتِ، وَمِثْلُهُنَّ العَفِيفُونَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَيَدْرَأُ}</span> ... يَدْفَعُ العُقُوبَةَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِالْإِفْكِ}</span> ... أَشْنَعِ الكَذِبِ، وَهُوَ رَمْيُ أُمِّ المُؤْمِنِينَ عَائِشَةَ رَضِيَ اللهُ عَنْهَا بِالزِّنَى.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عُصْبَةٌ مِّنكُمْ}</span> ... جَمَاعَةٌ مِنْكُمْ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَوَلَّى كِبْرَهُ}</span> ... تَحَمَّلَ مُعْظَمَهُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَفَضْتُمْ فِيهِ}</span> ... خُضْتُمْ فِيهِ مِنْ حَدِيثِ الإِفْكِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَلَقَّوْنَهُ}</span> ... تَتَلَقَّفُونَهُ، وَتَنْقُلُونَهُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بُهْتَانٌ}</span> ... كَذِبٌ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَعِظُكُمُ}</span> ... يَنْهَاكُمْ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٢١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خُطُوَاتِ الشَّيْطَانِ}</span> ... طُرُقَهُ، وَمَذَاهِبَهُ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
